{"tid":2005189,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《報復性消費的爆買熱潮》中國轉賣商再次現身藥妝店 日本經濟停滯正是掃貨好時機？","createTime":"2020-05-07T03:03:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T03:42:04.000Z","uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dace4de3de7d78e71c6f04e202121fedab2a11f6","tid":2005189,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKCYrqSb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKCYrqSb.jpg&h=566e43f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自從肺炎疫情在全球爆發以後，外國人觀光客的身影就徹底消失在日本的街頭，然而消失的不只是觀光客，還有原本常常跑單幫的代購商、轉賣商。如今日本的疫情都還沒有趨緩，日本記者卻發現這些商人已經再次出現在東京的藥妝店，大肆搜刮日本製造的化妝品！根據調查這一箱又一箱的化妝品正是要供應給中國的「報復性消費」，由於日本經濟停滯導致商品價格低廉，正是轉賣商大賺一筆的好時機啊～～<br />\n<br />\n日本記者發現東京出現了熟悉的景象&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKCYrKQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKCYrKQ.jpg&h=e8bd96a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n東京雖然已經發布將近一個月的「緊急事態宣言」，最近還是有一天破百人確診武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒）的情況，看起來疫情短期還無法得到控制。就在人們避免外出、避免群聚的情況下，朝日電視台的記者卻捕捉到東京的藥妝店附近有一群人聚在一起&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"c24ab0019b79aba47a8e15b9cfdcd43141606516","tid":2005189,"uid":169310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:06:45.000Z","msg":"走資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那就係唔想你班仆街走資，自己地方唔洗錢，走去人地地方幫人消費"},{"pid":"0a3201fdf325bb73ac50082ece97cd5c5aec1440","tid":2005189,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:07:40.000Z","msg":"兩人似乎在分裝什麼東西<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKCYrKY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKCYrKY.jpg&h=3b588d10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKCYrac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKCYrac.jpg&h=388aca98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來又有一些人提著大量化妝品過來<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKCYrag.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKCYrag.jpg&h=bcc0c462&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKCYrak.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKCYrak.jpg&h=eb6fd12d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這時有一輛廂型車靠近<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKCYrao.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKCYrao.jpg&h=6f25dfd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n眾人陸續將地上的物品搬上車<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKCYras.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKCYras.jpg&h=4431fbb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來車子繼續在路邊停靠半小時，好像在等著什麼？<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKCYraw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKCYraw.jpg&h=c07bf549&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這群人似乎都用中文交談<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKCYraSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKCYraSY.jpg&h=a9678d3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後又有人提著大量紙袋過來了！<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKCYrqSZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKCYrqSZ.jpg&h=00460b31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這一連串的行為正是所謂的「爆買」，也就是轉賣商在日本大量掃貨賣到國外牟利的行為。爆買本身是已經存在好幾年的現象，然而因為肺炎疫情消失了一陣子，最近又突然冒了出來才會引發媒體關注&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n在一家藥妝店爆買20多箱商品！<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKCYrqSa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKCYrqSa.jpg&h=d8e1441a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKCYrqSb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKCYrqSb.jpg&h=566e43f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記者詢問了中國網購業者，他們坦承最近對於日本製商品的需求的確爆增！<br />\n<br />\n「現在中國陸續解除封城」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKCYrqSc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKCYrqSc.jpg&h=9ac44367&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「開始出現熱絡的報復性消費」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKCYrqSd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKCYrqSd.jpg&h=90014a7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「報復性消費」指的是透過花錢紓解悶了好幾個月的壓力<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKCYrqSe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKCYrqSe.jpg&h=5cab4ae0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d23d35b6c58e57c999cfce2863e58e97055b8bd","tid":2005189,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:10:12.000Z","msg":"封城解除以後開始爽快花錢！<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKCYrqSf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKCYrqSf.jpg&h=d2244d03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本製商品的需求量暴增，但是民眾無法自己到日本購買！<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKCYrqSg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKCYrqSg.jpg&h=1e8e4d9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記者嘗試接觸這些在藥妝店搬貨的人&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n記者：「你們在做什麼？（日文）」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKCYrqWX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKCYrqWX.jpg&h=1f8f5d40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男性：「我不懂日文（日文）」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKGbrKQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKGbrKQ.jpg&h=e0f06182&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記者隔天再去察看，又見到同樣的景象<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKGbrKU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKGbrKU.jpg&h=64ba6f78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國網購業者透露，現在受到日本出入境限制與隔離規定的影響，一般中國民眾很難自己去日本購買商品，這就造成轉賣的商品非常搶手。而且日本國內的消費停滯，商品價格下跌，轉賣商能夠大幅壓低進貨成本，是能夠大撈一筆的好機會啊！<br />\n<br />\n「這是千載難逢的機會」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKGbrKY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKGbrKY.jpg&h=33157a37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「日本陷入停滯，商品價格變得很便宜」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKGbrKc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKGbrKc.jpg&h=27183582&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「就可以用低廉的價格大量買進好東西了啊」<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/27/97/qJeZpaKblKGbrKg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F27%2F97%2FqJeZpaKblKGbrKg.jpg&h=a3523b78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c898045ee170f05811b17db88132cce4acfdd16","tid":2005189,"uid":45523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:38:17.000Z","msg":"一幅圖一句解釋非常易睇"},{"pid":"8dd5c6fd5ca3a59e911c086c129814189603bd77","tid":2005189,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:39:24.000Z","msg":"香港人準備藥房多過以前未"},{"pid":"6a60b68c24803602d93683cfc3f463ae13e729dd","tid":2005189,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c24ab0019b79aba47a8e15b9cfdcd43141606516","tid":2005189,"uid":169310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:06:45.000Z","msg":"走資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那就係唔想你班仆街走資，自己地方唔洗錢，走去人地地方幫人消費"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:42:04.000Z","msg":"咁拎返中國賣，呢部份咪係中國經濟，個水貨商人賺咗錢有冇交返稅就唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}